"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:7.4.6\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">7.4.6</span> 標題：鼓、手鼓、框鼓（drum, hand drum, frame drum）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： תֹּף, תפף</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： tof, tafaf（動詞）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:27\">GEN 31:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:20\">EXO 15:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:20\">EXO 15:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:34\">JDG 11:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:5\">1SA 10:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:6\">1SA 18:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:5\">2SA 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr13:8\">1CH 13:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:12\">JOB 21:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:26\">PSA 68:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:3\">PSA 81:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:3\">PSA 149:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:4\">PSA 150:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:12\">ISA 5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:8\">ISA 24:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:32\">ISA 30:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:4\">JER 31:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： τύμπανον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： tumpanon)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt3:7\">JDT 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt16:1\">JDT 16:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc9:39\">1MA 9:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd5:2\">1ES 5:2</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0953_tambourine.png\" alt=\"手鼓（樂器）\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">手鼓（樂器） (© Public Domain - Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>鼓由一塊膜和一個扁圓形、三角形或方形的框架組成；膜通常由動物皮做成，在框架上張緊固定。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>根據放置鼓的位置，擊鼓者可以用一隻或兩隻手來擊打。擊鼓者可以左手持鼓，把鼓放在左臂下，或者靠在胸前，然後用右手擊打；也可以把鼓放在膝蓋上或地上，然後用一隻或兩隻手擊打。用右手手掌擊鼓時，可以用左手手指來加緊或放鬆鼓面上的張力。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0516_drum.jpg\" alt=\"敲打手鼓的婦女\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">敲打手鼓的婦女 (Gary Todd, Israel Museum, CC0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>希伯來文<em>tof</em> 的出現場合通常與歌唱、遊行或節期有關。考古證據表明，框架上帶金屬圓箍的鼓（「鈴鼓」或「小手鼓」）在聖經時期並不為人所知。一般來說，這個詞最好譯成「手鼓」或「鼓」。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
